<s> The shorter length of most of the names is good.  </s>
<s> I really don't understand why x and y size for the display were separated.  </s>
<s> I can't really see caching using Vary based only on x or y.  </s>
<s> So, I'd suggest: UA-pix: x-size x y-size because it's shorter and no significant loss of functionlity.  </s>
<s> I also don't understand the rationale behind UA-media- type introducing many extra header names, instead of UA-media: type which seems like it works just as well conceptually, and fits perfectly into Vary based caching.  </s>
<s> Bottom line -- I'd like it to be more like it was before, but with the shorter names.  </s>
