<s> The new draft of draft-mutz-http-attributes is now available at: ftp://ds.internic.net/internet-drafts/draft-mutz-http-attributes-01.txt  </s>
<s> Most of the syntax changes in the draft are to provide compliance with the transparent content negotiation method for features described in: draft-holtman-pre02-19.txt.  </s>
<s> It's not possible to supply more than one numeric argument, or any non-numeric argument to features.  </s>
